---
title: Zucchini Noodle Lasagna
description: We love indulging in Grandma’s lasagna every once in a while, but this lighter zucchini noodle version is a dish you can enjoy any night of the week. Our version has all the cheesy, meaty flavour of the original, without that nap-inducing heaviness.
